    "The KoLA dataset encompasses 2,138 English test instances, assessing LLMs' capacity to rationally deduce and generate knowledge at four hierarchical levels: memory, comprehension, application, and innovation.",
    "To ensure impartiality, the evaluation employs standardized scores and a comparative assessment system, with quarterly dataset updates implemented to mitigate the potential for model impropriety.",
    "• LLMEVAL-2 (Zhang et al, 2023e).",
    "The LLMEVAL-2 dataset comprises 480 Chinese questions that assess knowledge across different domains.",
    "The questions, sourced from external databases spanning 12 domains, encompass both multiplechoice and open-ended formats."
